  "intent": "Execute a serial dilution protocol using DMSO as diluent across two 96-well plates. First, dispense calculated DMSO volumes (n\u00d72.4\u00b5L) to columns 2-12 of plate 1 and all columns of plate 2. Transfer compound stock (n\u00d77.2\u00b5L) to column 1 of plate 1. Perform 1:3 serial dilutions by transferring n\u00d74.8\u00b5L between consecutive columns across both plates, mixing 6 times at 90% total volume after each transfer, creating a continuous 22-point dilution series.",
